HEADWORD: Muck
<hw>Muck</hw> <pr>(m⟦ucr⟧k)</pr>, <pos>adv.</pos> <def>Abbreviation of
<xex>Amuck</xex>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><cs><col><b>To run a muck</b></col>. <cd>See
